{"tid":559243,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 班蘭椰汁年糕","createTime":"2018-02-13T04:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T04:48:39.000Z","uid":30742,"like":51,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"632d21df11f1abb2f705564589ee419a870258c9","tid":559243,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T04:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/4OAFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2F4OAFM.jpg&h=88e2f813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/syeSOJTB2Pc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsyeSOJTB2Pc&d=hAob8PXt6f46nKZTGsFS6ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=54007e4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/syeSOJTB2Pc</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然時間好似有d倉促，<br />\n但上個weekend我整完之後真係覺得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以拿拿臨剪好條片就post上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個真係好香班蘭味，蒸完滿室班蘭香<br />\n而且多謝舅母送左包稀少糖比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n我試左用黎整，一樣好夠香甜，連糖尿人士都應該岩食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果普通用冰糖一樣得，份量都係一樣<br />\n呢個新年一定要試試佢！包你滿意！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班蘭椰汁年糕 圖文食譜: <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/02/pandan-coconut-new-year-rice-cake.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F02%2Fpandan-coconut-new-year-rice-cake.html&d=hAob8PXt6f46nKZTGsFS6ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=7d458832\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/02/pandan-coconut-new-year-rice-cake.html</a><br />\nFacebook專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=hAob8PXt6f46nKZTGsFS6ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=23719899\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=hAob8PXt6f46nKZTGsFS6ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=a0b662ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=hAob8PXt6f46nKZTGsFS6ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=5609d7d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"df8ad1d7ae799dcf44013f0299e86b064fb1022a","tid":559243,"uid":34489,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T04:23:09.000Z","msg":"頭香 我要食老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1652f5c159d1c49a19127276e0b137f05376a9a0","tid":559243,"uid":16477,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T04:37:02.000Z","msg":"新年快樂 老娘"},{"pid":"71f2915c9a194a077f14b60a2041b2e7419a0bc7","tid":559243,"uid":73356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T04:41:55.000Z","msg":"老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c01586c390e45ccc03592899f4faca0a46c84fa","tid":559243,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"df8ad1d7ae799dcf44013f0299e86b064fb1022a","tid":559243,"uid":34489,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,